Package smac.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Config
    Config defines the configuration settings of the SMAC daemon.
    InputQueue
    InputQueue defines a queue that is being monitored by the SMAC daemon.
    OutputQueue
    OutputQueue defines a queue that is being used as an output channel by the SMAC daemon.
    RoutingTask
    RoutingTask defines the details of a task that must be carried out by the SMAC daemon.
    Rule
    Rule class defines a rule which is used by the SMAC daemon to route an incoming message to an outgoing queue.
